The paper deals with ranked enumeration of answers to full conjunctive queries, which is a problem in the field of databases (cs.DB). The authors also mention the use of dynamic programming algorithms (cs.DS) and ranking functions (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the time complexity of the algorithms used (cs.DC) and the tradeoff between different enumeration approaches (cs.CC).
